(iii) The undertaking of Unit-16 of the Company located at TSIIC, SEZ, Polepally Village, Jadcherla Mandal, Mahbubnagar district, Telangana, transferred to Wytells Pharma Private Limited, a wholly owned step-down subsidiary of the Company and 100% subsidiary of Eugia Pharma Specialities Limited  w.e.f June 1, 2021.  &lt;BR&gt; 
